          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "# GesturesXV\n\n## iPhone X gestures brought to older iPhones\n\nGesturesXV brings the modern gesture navigation from iPhone X to older iPhone models compatible with iOS 15.\n\n## Features\n\n- iPhone X-style gesture navigation\n- Swipe up to go home\n- Swipe up and hold for App Switcher\n- Swipe from bottom corners for Back\n- Smooth animations\n- Highly customizable\n- Low battery impact\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- iOS 15.0 and later\n- Older iPhone models (non-X devices)\n\n## Note\n\nThis tweak requires a respring after installation. Some gestures may need time to get used to if you're coming from Android or newer iOS devices.",
